; Coverage test for draft.cc @@ total cost handling
; When a draft template posting has a cost with the @@ operator,
; the code takes a different branch than @ (not per-unit).
; Exercises:
;   L457: if (post.cost) -- entering cost handling
;   L463: if (*post.cost_operator == "@") -- false branch
;   L474-476: new_post->cost = *post.cost

2024/01/01 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    10 AAPL @@ $50.00
    Assets:Cash   $-50.00

test xact 2024/06/15 Grocery to Expenses:Food '@@' '$60.00' '10 AAPL' from Assets:Cash
2024/06/15 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food                            10 AAPL
    Assets:Cash
end test
